<command> --help     universal help command
info <command>	     info about command
man <command>	     manual about command


//man is categorised in many sections
man 5 passwd	    man of section 5 for passwd commad


1	exexutable program and file format
2	system call provided by the kernel
3	library call probided by program lib
4	device files (usually stored in /dev)
5	file formats
6	games
7	miscellaneous (macro package, convensions etc)
8	sys admin command (prog run by sudo)
9	kernel routines


